{
  "chapter": 26,
  "chapter_summary": "第二十六回「迷情」。西湖月夜，风四娘见萧十一郎扶冰冰上楼，心中酸楚。沈璧君亦心事重重。王猛来寻失踪的史秋山，侯一元认出风四娘。王猛疑史秋山落水，跳湖搜寻。楼上，萧十一郎与冰冰独处，风四娘与沈璧君闯入。四人相见，气氛尴尬。风四娘以笑语打破僵局，众人饮酒。风四娘追问冰冰胎记之事，冰冰承认，并说此秘密只有母亲和大哥逍遥侯知道。萧十一郎与风四娘讨论逍遥侯可能未死：那瞎子武功奇诡，能随意扭曲关节（瑜珈），面目浮肿可能因误食金柯萝，且瞎子知道冰冰的胎记秘密。萧十一郎推测逍遥侯练成了「九转还童脱胎换骨无相神功」，重伤散功后恢复原形。风四娘提及天宗与养狗的人，以及杜吟带她上八仙船的经历。萧十一郎讲述萧十二郎不肯带他上八仙船，改带他去救冰冰的经过。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们现在就上去找她好不好？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "风四娘忍不住",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你找什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_meng",
      "speaker_name": "王猛",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们的老二。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "王猛又在",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "史老二呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "我怎么知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我怎么知道。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "喃喃",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "难道他会跟别人一起走了？",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你为什么不进去看看？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_meng",
      "speaker_name": "王猛",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你呢？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我有我的事，你管不着。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_meng",
      "speaker_name": "王猛",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为什么她们是例外？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_meng",
      "speaker_name": "王猛",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你知道她们是谁？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hou_yi_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "侯一元",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你也听说过这个女人？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_meng",
      "speaker_name": "王猛",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你怎么认出她的？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_meng",
      "speaker_name": "王猛",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "还有个女人是谁？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_meng",
      "speaker_name": "王猛",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你看见史老二没有？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_meng",
      "speaker_name": "王猛",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "刚才还看见的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_meng",
      "speaker_name": "王猛",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "现在他的人呢？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_meng",
      "speaker_name": "王猛",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他有没有在那条渡船上？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_meng",
      "speaker_name": "王猛",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我没有看见他上去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "厉声",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你究竟想说什么？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "风四娘也在盯着她",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你身上真的有块青色的胎记？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "幸好我总算还是听出了你的声音。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 219,
      "line_end": 219
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好酒。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 243,
      "line_end": 243
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这是三十陈年的女儿红。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 253,
      "line_end": 253
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "她笑着",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "喝这种酒应该配洋澄湖的大闸蟹。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 255,
      "line_end": 255
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我去替你蒸螃蟹。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 257,
      "line_end": 257
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我也去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 259,
      "line_end": 259
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "对螃蟹，我也比你内行。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 259,
      "line_end": 259
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "真的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 317,
      "line_end": 317
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "风四娘却还要",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这块胎记真在……在他说的那地方？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 319,
      "line_end": 319
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "风四娘立刻抢着",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 339,
      "line_end": 339
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我大哥。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 341,
      "line_end": 341
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "逍遥侯？天公子？哥舒天？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 343,
      "line_end": 343
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "嗯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 345,
      "line_end": 345
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "可是，你大哥岂非也死了？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 357,
      "line_end": 357
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你大哥死了后，这秘密岂非已没有人知道？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 361,
      "line_end": 361
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "没有什么。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 375,
      "line_end": 375
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "风四娘笑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "难道你们认为逍遥侯还没有死？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 377,
      "line_end": 377
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎忽然",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 399,
      "line_end": 399
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你没有想到过，也许他并不是天生的侏儒。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 405,
      "line_end": 405
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "她问",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你为什么要这么样想？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 407,
      "line_end": 407
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但他却明明是个侏儒。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 413,
      "line_end": 413
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "忽又问",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你有没有听说过道家的元婴？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 415,
      "line_end": 415
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但那也只不过是神话而已。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 425,
      "line_end": 425
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那的确只不过是神话。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 427,
      "line_end": 427
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但神话并不是完全没有根据的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 429,
      "line_end": 429
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么根据？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 431,
      "line_end": 431
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "萧十一郎道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 435,
      "line_end": 435
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你看见过这种功夫？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 439,
      "line_end": 439
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 441,
      "line_end": 441
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "所以这种功夫也只不过是传说而已。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 443,
      "line_end": 443
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "传说更不会没有根据。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 445,
      "line_end": 445
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "所以你认为逍遥侯已练成了这种功夫？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 447,
      "line_end": 447
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "他接着又",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他接着又道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 463,
      "line_end": 463
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "嗯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 471,
      "line_end": 471
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "难",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "难道你真的认为那瞎子就是逍遥侯？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 483,
      "line_end": 483
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "很可能。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 485,
      "line_end": 485
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你凭哪点认为很可能？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 487,
      "line_end": 487
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "据说这种功夫叫'瑜珈'。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 495,
      "line_end": 495
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "瑜珈！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 497,
      "line_end": 497
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这两个字是天竺语。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 499,
      "line_end": 499
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那瞎子练的是天竺武功？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 501,
      "line_end": 501
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "还有呢？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 507,
      "line_end": 507
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "吃了金柯萝的人，就一定会变成那样子？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 517,
      "line_end": 517
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不死就会变成那样子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 519,
      "line_end": 519
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "你知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你知道的事好像比以前多得多了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 521,
      "line_end": 521
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这两年来我看了不少书。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 523,
      "line_end": 523
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这两年来，我的武功也确实进步了些。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 529,
      "line_end": 529
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那瞎子好像也这么样说过。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 531,
      "line_end": 531
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "又",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他眼睛发着光，又道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 535,
      "line_end": 535
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎没有再",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一加一等于二",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 543,
      "line_end": 543
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "养狗的人？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 549,
      "line_end": 549
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "风四娘也知道他不懂",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "养狗的人，就是天宗的宗主。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 551,
      "line_end": 551
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你也知道天宗？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 553,
      "line_end": 553
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我看的书虽不多，知道的事却不少。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 555,
      "line_end": 555
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "我不但知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我不但知道天宗，还知道天宗的宗主养了条小狗。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 561,
      "line_end": 561
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "你怎么知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你怎么知道的？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 563,
      "line_end": 563
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "当然是有人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "当然是有人告诉我的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 565,
      "line_end": 565
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 567,
      "line_end": 567
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "杜吟。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 569,
      "line_end": 569
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "杜吟是什么人？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 571,
      "line_end": 571
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "杜吟就是带我到八仙船去的人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 573,
      "line_end": 573
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "八仙船？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 575,
      "line_end": 575
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "难道你不知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "难道你不知道八仙船？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 579,
      "line_end": 579
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 581,
      "line_end": 581
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你也没有到八仙船去过？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 583,
      "line_end": 583
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 585,
      "line_end": 585
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你还记不记得他们要在一条船上请你喝酒？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 591,
      "line_end": 591
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那条船就是八仙船。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 595,
      "line_end": 595
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "可是我并没有到他们那条船上去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 597,
      "line_end": 597
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 599,
      "line_end": 599
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为来带路的人，忽然又不肯带我去了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 601,
      "line_end": 601
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 603,
      "line_end": 603
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为他怕我被人暗算，他不想看着我死在他面前。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 605,
      "line_end": 605
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他是谁？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 607,
      "line_end": 607
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "就是那个送信去的少年。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 609,
      "line_end": 609
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "萧十二郎？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 611,
      "line_end": 611
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "她微笑着又",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她微笑着又道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 617,
      "line_end": 617
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他不肯带你到八仙船去，带你到哪里去了？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 625,
      "line_end": 625
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "带我去找一个人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 627,
      "line_end": 627
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "冰冰？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 26,
      "line_start": 629,
      "line_end": 629
    }
